SECTION 1. The following barrios are hereby created in the Municipality of Catarman, Province of Samar:

Barrio of Guba, consisting of the sitios of Cag-oange, Guba, Colarema, Loyagay, Catangbo-an and Boc-sol;

Barrio of Hibolwangan, consisting of the sitios of Talahid, Deit, Talorag-on, Maghepid, Somalog, Boy-an, Cag-agengay and Cantnaria;

Barrio of Cal-egang, consisting of the sitios of Cal-egang, Mag-agong-ong, Guinperahan, Gebabao-gan, Pelit and Banijet;

Barrio of Liberty, consisting of the sitios of Hapnit, Poyao, Bango, Caangyapan and Uppeo;

Barrio of Bayho, consisting of the sitios of Her-tigan, Taloto-an, Cabato-an and Lower Caynaga;

Barrio of Paticua, consisting of the sitios of He-manalod, Awang, Nagcahog, Olaogan and Sumalog;

Barrio of Gulatan, consisting of the sitios of Baga, Kaglangboy, Babaras and Palanas;

Barrio of Genatad, consisting of the sitios of Cag-libas, San-og, Catoto-ogan and Camogdan;

Barrio of Daganas, consisting of the sitios of Segad, Suga, Iraya Suga, Benog, Wate, Oway, Tamburosan, Mametin and Lib-jo;

Barrio of Macagtas, consisting of the sitios of Pelit, Balud, Caraja-an and Macopa;

Barrio of Macagtas, consisting of the sitios of Pelit, Balud, Caraja-an and Macopa;

Barrio of Gebulwangan, consisting of the sitios of Kinaatban, Caboyu-an, Maghipid, Di-it, Nabawang, Boy-an Cag-angingay and Somalog;

Barrio of Cag-abaca, consisting of the sitios of Cagbabahe, Iba, Caganahao, Oson, Son-og, Cabatangan, Guimpohagan, Candanda, Cabadia√±gan and Ca-angyapan;

Barrio of Upper Caynaga, consisting of the sitios of Tura and Cabalocawi-an;

Barrio of Getigo,. consisting of the sitios of Ma-hagna, Panaghiran, Ca-olayanan, Salimpawod, Patong and Hinaboyan; and

Barrio of Capipi-an, consisting of the sitios of Cag-omondong, Mangpang, Cababalayan, Cabalocawi-an and Pangi.
